 data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1395713</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:23:08.000Z","msg":"Facebook舐共我諗大家都略有所聞，<br />\n原來佢誇張到封人account 可以因為人地14年講過嘅嘢，有追溯期<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xb8pGMg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxb8pGMg.png&h=fa283d82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以今次Now被人刪片係好好既證據 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ppV0e6e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FppV0e6e.png&h=717a1f44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7eeXhjA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7eeXhjA.png&h=6922914b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但Facebook調查完竟然好無恥咁話：「相信是出於直播完成後上傳訊號的技術層面原因」<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n整左條新片，有中英對照，交代呢件事<br />\n一日未推到比外媒一日都唔會放棄<br />\n麻煩大家推又好share又好，有渠道比外媒又好，一齊搞掂佢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/aMrWnXKo15U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FaMrWnXKo15U&d=%2FAyHQi%2FQiMXiPJLA4RPCZhZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=b2ecc4f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/aMrWnXKo15U</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cPYtaeD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcPYtaeD.png&h=bb3a071b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EXVWi72.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEXVWi72.png&h=9c3920ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OWn2eGo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOWn2eGo.png&h=7e6490ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\nFacebook 政治審查？Now新聞7分鐘敏感片段消失於Facebook <br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n重點內容:<br />\n<br />\nNow新聞Facebook專頁內有7分鐘片段懐疑被Facebook刪除<br />\n<br />\n7月21日<br />\n-元朗暴徒攻擊市民<br />\n<br />\n7月22日凌晨（襲撃後同一個夜晚）<br />\n-警察調查元朗南邊圍村<br />\n-Now新聞於Facebook Live直播 (1:28am-4:47am)<br />\n-其後有人發現7分鐘的內容消失（03:55am 至 04:02am）<br />\n-消失的內容，包括警員（游乃強亦在內）與白衫疑兇在村公所密會（4:01am）<br />\n<br />\nNow新聞確認：<br />\n當日是不經刪剪地在Facebook Live進行直播<br />\n<br />\nFacebook回應：<br />\n-「Facebook Live直播功能也不存在被內容發佈者中間抽起或剪接的可能性」<br />\n-7分鐘的內容消失的原因「相信是出於直播完成後上傳訊號的技術層面原因」"},{"pid":"6e9f94c88f10eb648f2b744e3715567198fae17a","tid":1425913,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18ad93adbcb792f88473e6eda7e036f8229c03ee","tid":1425913,"uid":301258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5dfaee12cd6f572590ae205b6587fe601ee6184","tid":1425913,"uid":228894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a4d04e6f62cb63c11b208c00c15978f45e2a913","tid":1425913,"uid":301258,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T23:38:33.000Z","msg":"好有可能 中共已經攞左資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n轉用twitter/reddit 啦<br />\n起碼唔奶共"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T23:40:00.000Z","msg":"IG會唔會舔埋野架.....<br />\n我靠IG睇J圖架......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:21:29.000Z","msg":"唔係掛<br />\nJ 圖都唔俾睇<br />\n全港男人打仗都似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:26:07.000Z","msg":"J 圖都唔俾睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我即刻 Full Gear 自製菠蘿 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9785ec6f51e4de743fa7ff476e685b8e23d655fd","tid":1425913,"uid":49078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:53:08.000Z","msg":"係咪冇得解返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce80ce2ce1a5abf2d50f4573464debdca9a1996b","tid":1425913,"uid":22